~Genres~
Animation | Adventure | Comedy | Crime | Family | Sci-Fi

~Storyline~
While Gru, the ex-super-villain is adjusting to family life and an attempted honest
living in the jam business, a secret Arctic laboratory is stolen. The Anti-Villain
League decides it needs an insider's help and recruits Gru in the investigation.
Together with the eccentric AVL agent, Lucy Wilde, Gru concludes that his prime
suspect is the presumed dead super-villain, El Macho, whose his teenage son is also
making the moves on his eldest daughter, Margo. Seemingly blinded by his
over-protectiveness of his children and his growing mutual attraction to Lucy, 
Gru seems on the wrong track even as his minions are being quietly kidnapped en masse 
for some malevolent purpose.

~Released~
July 3rd, 2013 (USA)
